{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/Divider3.png?t=1669381516\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Remote Play Together UPDATE!</h2>Thanks to Steam's newly added <strong>Remote Play Together</strong> functionality, online multiplayer is now available when playing S.U.B.!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/Divider2.png?t=1669381516\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay Information</h2>S.U.B. (Secret Underwater Base) is a <strong>2-player Local Cooperative Secret Agent Underwater Action Adventure game</strong>, fully made in an Arcade 8-bit visual- and audio style. Team up with a friend to infiltrate the Evil Doctor\u2019s secret underwater base; the fate of the world is in your hands!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Two gamemodes to explore (&quot;endless&quot; &amp; &quot;normal&quot;) while trying to halt the Evil Doctor's evil plans!<br></li><li>Gain access to the Secret Underwater Base using your state-of-the-art submarine!<br></li><li>Navigate through the dark using your sonar!<br></li><li>Hop into any role and/or task you want on the fly!<br></li><li>Upgrade and expand your submarine with better gadgets!<br></li><li>Always be wary of the evil doctor\u2019s minions! (Spoiler: there be robot sharks)<br></li><li>Explore your way through a fun mix of procedurally generated levels!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/Divider2.png?t=1669381516\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">History of S.U.B.</h2>S.U.B. was created during the 2017 Global Game Jam by Spreadable Fruit, a Dutch Indie game studio of 6 members total. We continued to polish the game into a more fleshed-out demo and then used the input from this demo to create the game you see before you right now!<br><br>~*~*~*<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/CharacterGiant2.png?t=1669381516\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/Character2Giant2.png?t=1669381516\" />*~*~*~<br><br>Thank you so very much for playing and upvoting our game; we look forward to hearing from you all!<br>Kind regards,<br>Team Spreadable Fruit<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/765140/extras/Divider2.png?t=1669381516\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Snorkel Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/69b6197aa99a9e1c6e434c1632605ca18b937790.jpg"},{"name":"Flipper Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/ecdd9e42e126ce5010864530649bb519013f1e53.jpg"},{"name":"Submarine Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/05f65e98632d46be7435f39912f4bbc23edfe569.jpg"},{"name":"Baby Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/89c74b5719f20058f3ec1b1647dd5fafc9b9e03d.jpg"},{"name":"In For The Long Haul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/4b45f943a1c3fe95a51cef0794ced4e40c4c60eb.jpg"},{"name":"I Can Wait And Fish All Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/41d857262fd803021806cc30a22a2407fff10043.jpg"},{"name":"All The Time In The Ocean","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/36fe5cef830c20118209c445872942be3f352576.jpg"},{"name":"Slowrun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/ed36d2e39359f022744e7611870031df7f3dc933.jpg"},{"name":"A Keycard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/765140/7b0a79f7f98ff2327ff9b925c614937cdb7e7b2f.jpg"},{"name":"A Pile Of Keycard